# BandOS Security

Read `.cursor/skills/bandos-security/SKILL.md` when changing auth, RLS, invitations, or public RPCs.

## Server actions (defense in depth)

Band-scoped mutations must call helpers from `src/lib/band/assert-access.ts`:

- `requireBandMember(bandId)` — read/write for any active member
- `requireBandAdmin(bandId)` — admin-only (profile, invites, public toggles)
- `requireSetlistMember` / `requireSongMember` / `requireEventMember` / `requireTodoMember` — when only resource id is passed
- `tryBandAdmin(bandId)` — JSON/error responses without redirect

Use returned `auth.supabase` instead of creating a new client.

## Redirects and URLs

- Post-auth paths: `sanitizeRedirectPath()` from `src/lib/safe-redirect.ts`
- External links: `sanitizeExternalUrl()` from `src/lib/safe-url.ts`
